    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Wieden &amp; Kennedy Names a Director</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Stuart Elliott</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Elliott, Stuart</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Wieden &amp; Kennedy names Matthew Seiler managing director in New York office, succeeding Tom Blessington, who returned to agency's headquarters in Portland, Ore, as group account director (Advertising column) (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Wieden &amp; Kennedy has named Matthew Seiler managing director at its New York office, succeeding Tom Blessington, who returned to the agency's headquarters in Portland, Ore., as a group account director on the 800.com account.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Wieden &amp; Kennedy has named Matthew Seiler managing director at its New York office, succeeding Tom Blessington, who returned to the agency's headquarters in Portland, Ore., as a group account director on the 800.com account.</p>
        <p>Mr. Seiler, 37, had been executive vice president and director for strategic services at BBDO New York, part of the BBDO Worldwide unit of the Omnicom Group. A successor to Mr. Seiler there has not been determined.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
